IINGREDIENTS LIST:

Sponge Pudding (74.5%) (Wheat, Egg, Milk), Butterscotch Sauce Sachet (24%) (Milk), Speculoos Crumb Sachet (1.5%) (Wheat).

Sponge Pudding [Wheat Flour [Wheat Flour, Niacin, Iron, Thiamin, Raising Agents (341, 500) Anticaking Agent (170)], Sugar, Margarine [Palm Oil, Rapeseed Oil, Palm Stearin, Water], Egg, Humectant (422), Fudge (4.5%) [Sugar, Glucose Syrup, Condensed Milk, Palm Fat, Salted Butter (Milk, Salt), Emulsifier (471), Humectant (422), Salt], Treacle [Cane Molasses, Partially Inverted Sugar Syrup], Natural Colour (150a), Raising Agents (341, 501, Sodium Carbonates), Ground Ginger, Acidity Regulator (330), Cinnamon, Preservative (Potassium Sorbate), Salt.

Butterscotch Sauce Sachet [Golden Syrup, Salted Butter [Milk, Salt], Soft Brown Sugar, Demerara Sugar, Water, Sweetened Condensed Milk [Milk, Sugar], Cream (Milk), Cornflour, Emulsifier (471), Salt, Natural Flavouring, Gelling Agent (440), Preservative (Potassium Sorbate)].

Speculoos Crumb Sachet [Wheat Flour, Sugar, Palm Oil, Rapeseed Oil, Sugar Syrup, Niacin, Iron, Raising Agent (Sodium Carbonates), Thiamin, Salt, Anticaking Agent (Calcium Carbonate), Cinnamon].

description: Vibrant, sticky and decadent, this spiced golden gingerbread sponge pudding is ready to be smothered with the smooth, rich butterscotch sauce. For the finishing touch, top with the spiced speculoos crumble for a true show stopper.
name: Gingerbread & Butterscotch Star Pudding
